WEBVTT

00:00.834 --> 00:03.026
<i>- Previously on Underground...
- What you doin' in here?</i>

00:03.045 --> 00:04.172
<i>She was sweepin' floors,</i>

00:04.206 --> 00:05.656
but she matched
the description of Harriet.

00:05.680 --> 00:06.615
Maybe you think

00:06.648 --> 00:08.150
this is your chance to escape.

00:08.183 --> 00:09.352
My boys.

00:09.384 --> 00:10.887
Not a day goes by I don't wonder

00:10.919 --> 00:12.787
<i>which one I let down more.</i>

00:12.820 --> 00:15.291
But I ain't sure I'm meant to lead.

00:15.323 --> 00:16.468
You put my baby in harm's way,

00:16.492 --> 00:17.894
<i>and you tricked me</i>

00:17.926 --> 00:19.603
into helping you do it.

00:20.062 --> 00:21.830
We're headed south.

00:21.864 --> 00:23.533
<i>You're dangerous,</i>

00:23.565 --> 00:26.009
and I can't have you staying
in my home anymore.

00:27.435 --> 00:28.435
Can I help you?

00:30.000 --> 00:36.074
Advertise your product or brand here
