You're awake.

41:44.378 --> 41:46.113
Good morning.

41:46.146 --> 41:47.849
Morning.

41:47.881 --> 41:50.150
It's chilly out there.

41:52.385 --> 41:56.189
Maybe you should just stay inside today.

41:58.091 --> 42:02.662
I'm tempted, but we're short
men at the armory today.

42:02.696 --> 42:04.498
I'll be missed.

42:04.530 --> 42:06.499
Yes.

42:06.533 --> 42:08.736
You will be missed.

42:14.341 --> 42:16.310
I'll see you tonight.

